Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢開始的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炫目的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.93,0:00:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪感覺冰涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小野花的香味很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有小孩子在哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經想不起當時的哭聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.82,0:01:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.17,0:01:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.31,0:01:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.65,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.79,0:01:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.16,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.96,0:02:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就來解決這長年的怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我不記得有與人結怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要躲開嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「唯一的小小的回憶」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.54,0:02:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.01,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.85,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐\N好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我成了壞人了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.53,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 妳怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.84,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身上都弄髒了\N祐一也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.14,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣丟下她不管吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去鋪床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想問這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祐一不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我可是被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.35,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己對我打過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你太遲鈍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是你不自覺的\N給別人帶來麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒見過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別欺負她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.42,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再問清楚也不遲吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管清不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是只有我自己忘了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的回憶我都記不起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吃的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了會吵到鄰居的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她在翻冰箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上來煮宵夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宵夜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一也來吃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好睏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睏了可以去睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血型？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的藝人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的都記不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會喪失記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要找藉口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說跟我有仇嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳喪失記憶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得有仇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼一看到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就有一把無名火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣窮追不捨的對她太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.12,0:07:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們應該也不相信她說的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.13,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些是她包包裡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了好多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了確認她的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她是不是喪失記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來似乎真有隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.09,0:08:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何朋友家人的線索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來似乎真有原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個今天都好早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天早起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是根本沒睡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們該不會是\N黏在一起開夜車吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉好紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以蹺課哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還說別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體好一點了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還得繼續請假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像臉色不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喪失記憶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是騙人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是離家出走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想回去也不能回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後騙取大人的同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闖蕩江湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很酷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喪失記憶 好像連續劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.14,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實跟連續劇是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我只顧著自己說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不要在外面閒晃比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不乖一點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會好的病都好不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩織 下次見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能像她一樣討人喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就不會那麼討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是問題不只是這種程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡會考 要好好記下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.70,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“蠢蛋 笨蛋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼喜歡考試嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“笨蛋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.49,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什麼深仇大恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不需要做到這種地步吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為這樣就沒事了\N真是大錯特錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來翻開課本的213頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.31,0:12:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記本等一下借你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳幹的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還把我的自動鉛筆拆開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮擦弄成碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.79,0:12:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.12,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.09,0:12:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我之前也幹過\N碰過這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳不要偷拿別人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放在制服的口袋裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天在學校要吃飯時\N卻不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說說看是誰拿的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 真的不知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的漫畫嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是進了你的房間沒錯\N但是錢包我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為我會相信妳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該出去的是妳吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 我有事情麻煩你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以來一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思要你陪我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的幫了我很大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有她的事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得麻煩了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也想要相信她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在做什麼都沒用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種大騙子 還是報警…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又撞到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.23,0:14:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你討厭我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有精神的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.81,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我寄住的親戚家的秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是月宮亞由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月宮亞由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉上有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個眼睛一個鼻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一果然討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭我了…\N我根本沒有這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我太多心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又吃了就跑了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正要去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我掉了東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢包嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 更重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我掉的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了？\N是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是很重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該要快點找到才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻想不起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候冷靜下來反而可以找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道要找的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就免談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 我支持妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那下次見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.06,0:16:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我還沒有介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是水瀨名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我名雪就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.44,0:16:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的表哥祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是騙人小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是偷錢包小姐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那種怪名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是澤渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有証據嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能証明妳真的叫做澤渡真琴嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要我叫妳的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就老實承認偷了錢包\N並且道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.48,0:17:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你說錢包？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她偷了我的錢包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天抱她去房間時掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你撿起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算待會拿給你卻忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.59,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不對 但是妳也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是妳先來找上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會發生這些事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且為什麼找上我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會跟妳結下樑子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認錯人了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.21,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且越說我越確定是你沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我忘了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.09,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是找到你的時候\N我想起了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.33,0:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我跟你有仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,線索就是你是祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,線索？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟祐一在一起\N說不定可以恢復記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她恢復記憶之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就先留在我們家吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.35,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們吃東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是真琴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的名字是澤渡真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 筆記本還我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記本借你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,筆記本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.04,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 明天去學校再還妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的筆記本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就去學校拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校應該關門了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有值班老師吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.13,0:20:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.33,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要呼吸外面的空氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為愚蠢的我\N誤以為她是小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我都要喘不過氣來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇社在練習嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.55,0:22:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是打擊惡魔之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.40,0:22:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.55,0:22:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.73,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.06,0:22:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.07,0:23:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.88,0:23:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.62,0:23:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.38,0:23:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在晚上的學校遇到的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與白天印象完全不同的面貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.95,0:23:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奪走了我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.49,0:23:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第4話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.52,0:23:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜裡
